comments: Took it online for a gen ed credit. Super easy course with discussion posts/quizzes on a near weekly basis, 2 exams, and an easy paper. Dr. Kushina used blackboard and email for everything and was always clear on what was due each week. She\'s also an incredibly kind person and tired to not "overwork" us even though the class was very low difficulty

comments: Kusina is really nice. Shes hilarious too. If you go to class, you will pass this class easily.
